<subSubSection pageId="271" pageNumber="876" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="271.[1453,2659,1239,1823]" pageId="271" pageNumber="876">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1454,1790,1598,1627]" pageId="271" pageNumber="876">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Tondano Rat has restricted distribution and has not been collected since 1932. It is probably threatened by deforestation and hunting for bushmeat markets. More research is needed to fully understand its natural history, population status, taxonomy, and conservation threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
